</P>
<P>
	The Sentinel also reported that as many as two of last season's  
four Magic assistants -- Brendan Suhr, Tom Sterner, Tree Rollins and 
Eric Musselman -- might be retained. 
</P>
<P>
	Rivers would succeed Chuck Daly, who retired May 24, after  
leading the Magic to a tie for the second-best record in the 
Eastern Conference this season. The team was eliminated from the 
playoffs in the first round by Philadelphia. 
  	   	
