<HEADLINE> Angels Put O'Brien on DL </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	ANAHEIM, Calif. (AP) -- Anaheim Angels catcher Charlie O'Brien  
was placed on the 15-day disabled list Friday because of a torn 
ligament and outfielder Reggie Williams was recalled from Triple-A 
Edmonton. 
</P>
